Rizopoulos, D. (2010) JM: An R Package for the Joint Modelling of Longitudinal and Time-to-Event Data. 
\emph{Journal of Statistical Software} \bold{35} (9), 1--33. \doi{10.18637/jss.v035.i09}
}

